high_descs: Turn right and look at the sink.
Pick up the green apple to the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave above the dishwasher.
Microwave the apple and then pick up the apple from the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the trash can to the right of the fridge.
Place the apple into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved green apple into the trash can.

high_descs: Turn towards your right and face the sink
Pick up the green apple on the sink
Turn around and walk to the microwave on your right above the stove
Open the microwave and place the apple inside, warm it up and remove it
Turn to the left and face the trash bin at the end of the counter
Place the apple in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Heat an apple in the microwave followed by throwing it away

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the green apple on the sink.
Turn around, move to the microwave on the right.
Heat the apple  in the microwave.
Take the heated apple out of the microwave and bring it to the trash can on the left of the microwave.
Put the heated apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the trash can.
